title: Machine Learning Engineer
bullets: Worked as a consultant for Key Three Data on a project aimed at developing an automated platform for converting first-person video to scene analytics.
Specialized in machine learning algorithms, clustering and analysis.
Deployed machine learning algorithms and integrated systems onto the Google Cloud Platform.
